sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 前端ApiClient
    participant Server as Express Server
    participant CSRF as CSRFMiddleware
    participant Auth as AuthRouter
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over Client,Server: 1. 首次加载页面
    Client->>Server: GET /api/auth/csrf-token
    Server->>CSRF: generateToken()
    CSRF-->>Server: csrfToken = crypto.randomBytes(32).hex
    Server->>Client: Response {csrfToken} + Set-Cookie: _csrf=xxx
    Client->>Client: apiClient.setCsrfToken(csrfToken)

    Note over Client,Server: 2. 登录
    Client->>Server: POST /api/auth/login {username, password} + X-CSRF-Token header
    Server->>CSRF: validate(req) — 比对 cookie._csrf === header.X-CSRF-Token
    CSRF-->>Server: valid=true
    Server->>Auth: authenticate user
    Auth->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>Auth: user record
    Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.compare + generateJWT
    Auth->>Client: Response {token, username, role} + Set-Cookie: _csrf=newToken

    Note over Client,Server: 3. 后续 mutating 请求
    Client->>Server: POST /api/records {data} + Authorization: Bearer JWT + X-CSRF-Token + Cookie: _csrf
    Server->>CSRF: validate(req)
    CSRF-->>Server: valid=true → next()
    Server->>Server: process request
    Server->>Client: Response {result}
